{"tid":2345299,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰副主席換人　新任國航黨委書記宋志勇接任","createTime":"2020-12-29T11:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T03:23:58.000Z","uid":50386,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6f552ae9de00d27e10fa047f14d871d6b3f674","tid":2345299,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"國泰航空（0293）今日（29 日）宣布，持國泰 3 成股份的中國國際航空公司董事長蔡劍江，辭任國泰副主席和非常務董事，由新任國航董事長、黨委書記宋志勇接替。<br />\n<br />\n現年 55 歲的宋志勇，現任國航（0753）董事長、黨委書記，於中國空軍第一飛行學院畢業。宋志勇在 1987 年加入國航，2010 年 12 月任中航集團公司黨組成員，2014 年 3 月起任國泰非執董，2016 年 12 月擔任中航集團公司副董事長、總經理、黨組副書記。國泰表示，宋志勇每年可收取 57.5 萬元董事酬金。<br />\n<br />\n通告又指，蔡劍江今日已經辭任國航董事長及非執行董事。國泰表示，蔡劍江自 2009 年 11 月底獲委任為公司董事，董事局衷心感謝他過往的工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/國泰副主席換人-新任國航黨委書記宋志勇接任\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%8F%9B%E4%BA%BA-%E6%96%B0%E4%BB%BB%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%AA%E9%BB%A8%E5%A7%94%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%E5%AE%8B%E5%BF%97%E5%8B%87%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGaF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=45b16432\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%8F%9B%E4%BA%BA-%E6%96%B0%E4%BB%BB%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%AA%E9%BB%A8%E5%A7%94%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%E5%AE%8B%E5%BF%97%E5%8B%87%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB&h=e2d1fb63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/國泰副主席換人-新任國航黨委書記宋志勇接任</a><br />\n因航好快有黨支部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6578dd87954cc2e480329ade52e5d4af41ea9b1","tid":2345299,"uid":45213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:40:47.000Z","msg":"之前果件都係黨委"},{"pid":"52192b44803b12547d9ddad38fd9e97f8c2bd9de","tid":2345299,"uid":59408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"國泰航空=國航<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"